reviewText: I was completely blown away by the information that Bill English provided in this presentation. His viewing of secret blue book report 13 and participation in the secret mission during the Vietnam War made what he had to say credible and very important. Another case of important information kept from people. I guess the UFO Hunters and cable channels didn't think that we needed to know about this!

Aside from poor production values, BOTH discs failed after 20 odd minutes running. Ran several other DVDs before and after (with no problem) so can only assume these discs at fault. Save your money. Would not recommend this DVD.
